This is the "Auction" smart contract Project with Remix IDE Solidity platform

All the codes have comments which able to provide detail explaintion.

Some Detail:
3 items, 4 bidders.

The creation address is the "Chairperson" who is the only one able to tell the winner by using the modifier condition.

Bidders able to register itself and able to vote their favoriate item from the Auction.

Every bidder have 5 tokens to vote and once used up, unable to provide more tokens unless start new auction.


